metadata.name: Desires of Emptiness
metadata.description:
Rebellious magic academy student Piraya have always strived for perfection and power, however knowing very well that the ultimate ancient knowledge that will reward her with all of what she desired will never come from her instructors, but from the forbidden texts that are hidden away from all to preserve balance and safety on the planet and the universe, Piraya sneaks at night in the magical academy to get hold of the ancient forbidden texts ...
